All done. Here's what was implemented:

**mrr-hl4.2 — JIRA link auto-injection in `gitlabadpt`**

- **`inject_jira.go`** (new): Three functions — `injectJiraLinksBackground` (fires goroutines after fetch), `maybeInjectJiraLink` (fetch desc → check marker → write), `appendJiraLink` (builds `---\n🎫 [KEY](url) <!-- mrboard -->`)
- **`gitlabadpt.go`**: Added `JiraInstanceURL string` to `Config`; calls `injectJiraLinksBackground` at the end of `FetchAll`  
- **`core.go`**: Passes `cfg.Jira.InstanceURL` to adapter config
- **`inject_jira_test.go`** (new): 8 tests covering idempotency (marker present = no-op), write paths (empty/non-empty desc), error propagation, and no-op guards (no URL, no JIRA ID)

The injection is fully non-blocking (`context.WithoutCancel` prevents cancellation from the next board refresh killing in-flight writes) and idempotent (the `<!-- mrboard -->` sentinel stops re-writes).

